* Iron Raptor growled as she suddenly felt something hit her back with massive force, she opens her mouth just in time to suddenly feel and see the launcher hit the ground and begin to fire at everything in front of it. Her knees are suddenly hit and she topples to the ground with a thud that shakes the earth, as the charges from the berserker launcher begin to hit her she heaves herself to her feet and tries to step out of it's firing range. The charges from the approaching Annihalator still managing to hit her repeatedly in the back, she suddenly snaps her head towards him and then whips her tail into the air, hoping that it would manage to strike the annoying Predacon.
She was sick of all of this and her anger was beginning to rise to an almost intolerable level, adrenaline pumping. She was sure that in a moment she would simply scrap them both, without thinking twice!*
